{"tid":1492623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要求撤回! 仆街順豐9月1又加價, 今次連紙箱膠袋都要收錢","createTime":"2019-08-21T02:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T17:15:01.000Z","uid":266569,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"db32dfb3b516525ea6b256f61aea75c70dd25fea","tid":1492623,"uid":266569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T02:15:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">陳茂波同林鄭話而家經濟倒退，人地減價順豐就加價, 紙箱運費平時$28,9月將會加到$54＋額外既紙箱費$20，即係要比$74</span></span><br />\n<br />\n5月果陣已加左1次價，而家短短4個月內又加<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />由$22加到$30以上！越重加得越多，起碼加1倍！包裝物料額外收$4-20<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pd0aeyh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpd0aeyh.jpg&h=9c28c91d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ivDi7Ti.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FivDi7Ti.jpg&h=1fed7171&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xQsPu6E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxQsPu6E.jpg&h=5fc84272&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M6GgUyk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM6GgUyk.jpg&h=b7c9582b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係fb仲要加價可以講到變減價咁, 比人屌到仆街, 一於去順豐fb屌佢老母！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1452573198380342/posts/2137835043187484/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1452573198380342%2Fposts%2F2137835043187484%2F&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41BV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=021f44d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1452573198380342/posts/2137835043187484/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/erWpi37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FerWpi37.jpg&h=84eff4ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na